### [NEW] [src/plugins/if_plugin.rs](file:///Users/zhanghu/vpn/clean-dns/src/plugins/if_plugin.rs)
- Config:
    ```yaml
    if: "provider:some_matcher"
    exec: [...]
    else_exec: [...]
    ```
- Logic:
    ```rust
    if cond.check(ctx) {
        exec.run(ctx)
    } else {
        else_exec.run(ctx)
    }
    ```

